#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/flow_obstacles.rst:72
#: 34186e453c254174bd19d8b49e51ab78
msgid ""
"Under the hood, ``MeshGen`` defers to Gmsh's OpenCASCADE backend for the "
"boolean operations and triangulation, then converts back into a "
":class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` with its internal element ordering. See "
":doc:`../../user_guide/meshes` for the full ``MeshGen`` API."
msgstr ""

